    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Oligopeptide-127 rh-Oligopeptide-4 is a single chain fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from rh-Oligopeptide-4 and Oligopeptide-127. The fusion peptide contains 55 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
